#- Chapter 3: Aftermath§0
§0
§0   With Otritus dead, the curse of the surrounding lands waslifted. The village and its descendents were safe and the people rejoiced. §0
§0
§0   However, there was no longer anyone to watch over and 
#- protect the seas.§0
§0
§0   Fullwit stepped up to the task and was crowned King Fullwit the God-Killer. Naturally, the new King would have difficultly ruling from his kingdom, as he does not naturally breathe water. So, he has endeavored to claim 
#- his court from the ocean with glass §0domes from which to rule over his new subjects.§0
§0
