#- Chapter 4: Claims§0
§0
§0   The Kingdom of §0
§0Abaddon claims §0
§0sovereignty over all §0
§0of the seas, rivers, §0
§0and lakes. The King §0
§0realizes that other §0
§0nations must use §0
§0these, but demands §0
§0that they respect the §0
§0waters and expects §0
§0their gratitude for §0

