#- Chapter 5: Policies§0
§0
§0   Abaddon is always §0
§0taking immigrants from §0
§0the topsoil. King Fullwit is always looking to increase harmony between the peoples of the land and the peoples of the sea. §0
§0
§0   Abaddon typically tries to avoid conflict, 
#- but will not hesistate §0to strike at those who disrespect the seas. The Kingdom will also maintain a standing force for defense. §0

